import React from "react"

export default function Meme()
{
	return (
		<main>
			<form className="form">
				<input 
					type="text"
					placeholder="Top text"
					className="form-input"
					/>
				<input 
					type="text"
					placeholder="Bottom text"
					className="form-input"/>
				<button className="form--button">Get a new meme image</button>
			</form>
		</main>
	)
}
